null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/cQR3VHRMUL8xGkWK5Up8rI7DHQD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":3,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/e9vJTJHkCOyBitE67n8zlp5Qm8q.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":3,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":1943,"height":1092,"file_path":"/55qVIFhykb6M6CGWRKQd9BsLI5D.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":3,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/4oIoe9tcSRzGSImp9Jqp1SKFwes.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/zajlFkhKugj9tqH57KHXpmTXIku.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/tSbZky1KLzqOSGPzYtqnxTQzNFy.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/hpP0ELkViFlU8PVWbEBvVx12YtJ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/bAXnki8lNZ9aaa4IujUj2IWhcqk.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/t9DvbIGimmOeynVbSCEUroBtEbl.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/mW16h0OkY2O5WMnsHH559AgwyQJ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/2JgAy850iNV2Gu4IJdmSpPxF8tE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/pmRtI4QvcBvXjw9mLOEAsV9Bq7i.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/r4aCiSa6AQA1k9nnfSUkfb3sQCS.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/HMr27rHck6JGEJuEsHxiTWFy0O.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2000,"height":1125,"file_path":"/wxMLr8eW9a0WSPsyNMBhxvurS2R.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1549,"height":872,"file_path":"/ht8u3HsgU5q67mJKgGDMJZH9j94.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.776,"vote_average":0},{"width":1914,"height":1078,"file_path":"/oBPrhvZwsa8BpWuK2dGIDZHbecx.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.776,"vote_average":0},{"width":3691,"height":2076,"file_path":"/rzeurRWgQqEUNgrt8o7k4XVGQND.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/aU3mWOFBEujrZXvjDUrr4dgyqN0.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/aUt4hdkGbTcMnb6reAAUUpTViX7.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/i8auucMFz8qi9GsxNVJbs4cDOX8.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1500,"height":844,"file_path":"/xV1AHNX9YOfzDYSKKMmSx4qHCtL.jpg","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":2400,"height":1350,"file_path":"/lxuMPNECpHzJGyLfk5calS3wRNT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:46:24.998+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":113,"tagline":"Could you kill your best friend?","homepage":"","overview":"In the future, the Japanese government captures a class of ninth-grade students and forces them to kill each other under the revolutionary \"Battle Royale\" act."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":122,"tagline":"Wenn dein bester Freund zu deinem Feind wird...","homepage":"","overview":"Japan, zu Beginn des neuen Milleniums. In den Schulen ist Brutalität und Gewalt an der Tagesordnung. Die Regierung sieht sich gezwungen, einzugreifen und ein Exempel zu statuieren. Ein Battle Royale-Gesetz soll die randalierenden Schüler wieder zur Raison bringen. Jährlich wird nun eine Schulklasse willkürlich ausgewählt und auf einer verlassenen Insel ausgesetzt. Die Regeln des Spiels sind simpel, aber gnadenlos: Jeder Teenager wird mit ausreichend Proviant sowie einer tödlichen Waffe ausgerüstet. Nach drei Tagen darf nur mehr ein einziger Überlebender auf der Insel auffindbar sein. Und so nimmt ein grauenvolles Abschlachten seinen Lauf. Denn wenn sie sich nicht fügen, werden alle unbarmherzig exekutiert."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"Hai mai ucciso il tuo migliore amico?","homepage":"","overview":"I giovani giapponesi sono troppo esagitati. Per disciplinarli viene emanato il Battle Royale Act: ogni anno una scolaresca viene estratta a sorte e catapultata su un'isola deserta. Sorvegliati dal prof. Takeshi e da un nucleo militare, gli studenti si giocano la \"battaglia reale\": ognuno riceve un'arma diversa, che sia un bazooka o una pinza per le ciglia, e si dà alla macchia. Scopo del gioco: eliminare tutti gli altri entro tre giorni. Regole: nessuna."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"42 élèves, trois jours, un survivant, pas de règles.","homepage":"","overview":"Dans un avenir proche, les élèves de la classe B de 3ème du collège Shiroiwa ont été amenés sur une île déserte par une armée mystérieuse. Un adulte surgit tout à coup devant eux : leur ancien professeur Kitano. Il leur annonce qu'ils vont participer à un jeu de massacre dont la règle consiste à s'entretuer. Seul le dernier des survivants pourra regagner son foyer. Kitano leur présente deux nouveaux élèves très inquiétants. Des coups de feu retentissent pour convaincre les incrédules. Selon la loi de réforme de l'éducation pour le nouveau siècle, ce sacrifice permettra de former des adultes sains. Abandonnés chacun à son sort avec de la nourriture et une arme, les adolescents disposent d'un délai de trois jours pour s'entretuer."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"¿Puedes matar a tu mejor amigo?","homepage":"","overview":"En el amanecer de un nuevo milenio, el país está al borde del colapso. Millones de personas vagan sin empleo. La violencia en la escuela está descontrolada y adolescentes rebeldes protagonizan boicots masivos. El gobierno contrataca con “Battle Royale”. Cada año, una clase es escogida al azar para que se enfrente, en una isla abandonada, a un cruel juego de supervivencia."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"大逃杀","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　为了培养出忠实效忠于成人、在逆境中坚忍不拔的青少年一代，日本政府出台《BR》法案。每年都从全国学校随机抽出一个班级的同学，前往荒岛进行生存极限挑战——老师发给学生地图、粮食和各式武器，令他们自相残杀，直到存活下来的最后一个，才能离开荒岛。接下来，残酷的游戏规则和令人绝望的生存条件，使班级里的年轻人开始了相互杀戮。善良或者凶残，主动出击或者被动防守， 同学们开始了各自的计划，人性的丑恶在血腥的死亡中暴露无遗。\r 　　大逃杀的游戏在荒岛上壮烈上演。究竟学生们的宿命如何，谁才是最后的存活者。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"Jen jeden může přežít!","homepage":"","overview":"Na přelomu tisíciletí se japonský národ zhroutil. Nezaměstnanost dosáhla obrovských hodnot, statisíce dětí bojkotovalo školu, dospělí ztráceli autoritu. Vláda jako nutnou reakci vymyslela „vzdělávací reformu tisíciletí“ - zákon Battle Royale. Každý rok vybírá jednu třídu, kterou násilím uvrhuje do děsivé hry, aby navodila mezi studenty strach a tím získala zpět ztracený respekt."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"Czy mógłbyś zabić swojego najlepszego przyjaciela?","homepage":"","overview":"Japonia w niedalekiej przyszłości. Kraj jest gospodarczą ruiną, rząd coraz częściej musi korzystać z pomocy wojska, żeby łagodzić społeczne niezadowolenie. Młodzi ludzie przestają kultywować wielowiekowe tradycje, zaczynają coraz głośniej buntować się przeciwko utrzymywaniu starzejącego się społeczeństwa. Aby uciszyć wszelkie głosy sprzeciwu, rządzący wymyślili całkiem skuteczny \"program naprawczy\". Co roku jedna z klas maturalnych, wybierana ze wszystkich japońskich szkół, jest przewożona na niewielką wyspę, gdzie w ciągu 72 godzin mają walczyć ze sobą do momentu aż zostanie jedna, żywa osoba. Ktoś taki zostaje zwycięzcą rządowego programu o nazwie \"Battle Royal\"..."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"Conseguias matar o teu melhor amigo?","homepage":"","overview":"Num futuro próximo, o Japão está à beira de um colapso económico. Milhões de pessoas encontram-se desempregadas, e não existe qualquer disciplina nas escolas. Como resposta à crise, o governo institui o programa Battle Royale para tentar controlar a crescente vaga de crimes juvenis. Depois de selecionada aleatoriamente uma turma de quarenta rapazes e raparigas com 15 anos, estes são raptados e enviados para uma ilha no meio do nada. Os estudantes são então obrigados a participar num jogo mortal sem regras, onde lhes é dada apenas uma arma, água e três dias para lutarem até à morte, até que um único sobrevivente saia vencedor. E se mais do que um estiver vivo depois do tempo limite, todos os concorrentes serão mortos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Королевская битва","runtime":113,"tagline":"Смогли бы вы убить своего лучшего друга?","homepage":"","overview":"Королевская битва — санкционированная правительством жестокая игра, в которой школьников заставляют участвовать под угрозой уничтожения. На необитаемом острове 42 старшеклассника на протяжении трёх дней будут безжалостно убивать друг друга с помощью случайных предметов и смекалки. Живым с острова вернётся только один."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een klas studenten wordt naar een klein geïsoleerd eiland gebracht. Daar aangekomen krijgen ze een kaart van het eiland, voedsel en verschillende wapens (de ene bruikbaarder dan de andere). Ze moeten gedurende drie dagen vechten met elkaar, zodat er één persoon overblijft. Ze krijgen allemaal een halsband die explodeert als ze de regels overtreden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":109,"tagline":"Skulle du kunna döda din bästa vän?","homepage":"","overview":"Skulle du kunna döda din bästa vän? 42 ungdomar ställs inför den frågan, innan de placeras på en öde ö där de inte har något annat val än att döda, eller dödas av sina kamrater. En fullständigt grotesk situation, där den enda som kommer att lämna ön är den som har överlevt slakten efter att ha mördat sin bästa vän, pojkvän eller flickvän. Alltihop övervakas av helikoptrar och datorer under ledning av den galne läraren och \"lekledaren\" Kitano."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Ölüm Oyunu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Yakın gelecekte Japonya'da, hükümet gençlerin neden olduğu şiddet eğlemlerinin önüne geçememektedir. Öğretmenler, aileler kısacası tüm toplum gençliğin yarattığı korku bulutuna teslim olmuştur. Japon hükümeti olayların kızışmasının ardından \"Battle Royale\" denilen kanunları kabul etmiştir. \"Battle Royale\" kanunlarına göre her yıl ülke içinden rastgele bir lise sınıfı seçilir ve bu sınıfın öğrencileri yerini yine hükümetten kimsenin bilmediği bir adaya götürülürler.\r Bu seneki \"Battle Royale\" için Nobu'nun sınıfı seçilir. Nobu ve arkadaşları hükümet tarafından \"Battle Royale\" adasına kaçırılırlar. Adada onları öğretmenleri Takeshi karşılar ve oynayacakları oyunun kurallarını açıklar. Kurallar basittir, Nobu ve 41 arkadaşından sadece bir kişi adadan canlı ayrılabilecektir. Hükümet gençlerin herbirine, içinde farklı silahlar ve yeterli yiyecek bulunan bir çanta verir. Gençler, adadan canlı çıkabilmek için 3 gün içinde birbirlerini öldürmek zorundadırlar..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Valahol, valamikor egy diktatórikus távol-keleti országban, az állami vezetők kegyetlen kísérletet eszelnek ki: negyvenkét középiskolást egy lakatlan szigeten arra kényszerítenek, hogy életre-halálra megvívjanak egymással. Géppisztolytól kezdve a sarlón át a konyhai étkészletből származó villáig, bármilyen fegyver a rendelkezésükre áll. A Programnak csak egyetlen túlélője lehet: a győztes. Takami Kósun regénye - melyet gyakran neveznek a 21. századi Legyek urának - botrányos karriert futott be. Bár megjelenését a japán kormány is ellenezte, a regény 1999 óta több kontinensen vezeti a sikerlistákat, számos feldolgozást ért meg."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":121,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Uuden vuosisadan alkaessa Japanin talous romahti, työttömyys kasvoi, ja samaan aikaan kun aikuiset menettivät tulevaisuudenuskonsa, lapsissa alkoi kasvaa halveksunta heitä kohtaan. Vanhempi sukupolvi alkoi pelätä nuorisoa ja kykenemättömänä ymmärtämään sen motiiveja enää lainkaan otti käyttöön todella radikaalin keinon: hallitus perusti taistelupeli Battle Royalen, jossa kerran vuodessa satunnaisesti valitun koululuokan oppilaat pakotetaan tappamaan toisensa siten, että vain yksi jää henkiin ja pääsee vapauteen.  Kilpailuun joutuu 42-henkinen yhdeksäs luokka, joka lähetetään autiolle saarelle. Siellä oppilaat saavat ruokaa, juomaa, kartan, kompassin ja sattumanvaraisen aseen, minkä jälkeen he lähtevät yksitellen ulos oppilasnumeron mukaisessa järjestyksessä. Jos kolmen vuorokauden kuluttua useampi kuin yksi oppilas on hengissä, heidät kaikki tapetaan."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"城岩学園3年B組の中学生たちは、修学旅行の名目で孤島へ。彼らの前に現われた担任教師キタノは、新世紀教育改革法、通称“バトル・ロワイアル（BR）法”により、殺し合いをさせると生徒たちに宣言。生還できるのは最後に生き残った1人だけだった。生徒たちはそれぞれ最低限の武器と食料を与えられ、3日間のサバイバルに追いやられる。男子生徒の七原と女子の中川は謎の転校生・川田と、なんとかこの窮地を脱する方法を探る。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"קרב מלכותי","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"הדרמה החזקה של קינג'י פוקאסקו מתרחשת בתחילתו של המילניום החדש, כאשר יפן עומדת על סף התמוטטות חברתית.כאשר אפילו ילדי בית הספר מתחילים לחבוט במערכת, הממשלה מציגה עונש חדש: קבוצת תלמידים אשר נבחרת רנדומלית, נלקחת לאי בודד, שם עליהם להלחם אחד בשני עד מוות."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Μια τάξη του λυκείου ξεκινάει για μια τυπική σχολική εκδρομή. Ξαφνικά όμως όλοι οι μαθητές ξυπνάνε σε ένα άγνωστο μέρος, με κάποια περίεργα περιλαίμια φορεμένα και δυο εντελώς ξένους και μυστηριώδεις τύπους δίπλα τους. Ο καθηγητής Κιτάνο τους υποδέχεται, και τους ενημερώνει πως αποτελούν την φετινή επιλογή για την εφαρμογή του Νόμου BR, ή αλλιώς Battle Royale. Όπου οι μονάδες μιας ολόκληρης τάξης θα αλληλοσκοτωθούν μεταξύ τους, μέχρι να μείνει ένας μόνο. Ενώ κάποιοι δείχνουν διατεθειμένοι να πατήσουν επί πτωμάτων για την επιβίωσή τους, ορισμένοι έχουν σκοπό να διατηρήσουν τα ιδανικά τους, έστω και αυτές τις περίεργες στιγμές. Τι είναι όμως αυτό που θα μπορέσει να δώσει το πλεονέκτημα, είτε στους μεν, είτε στους δε;"},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"배틀 로얄","runtime":0,"tagline":"오늘, 처음으로 친구를 죽였다","homepage":"","overview":"극심한 사회혼란을 겪고 있는 일본. 학급붕괴와 범죄에 노출된 청소년들을 강력한 생존 능력의 소유자로 만들기 신세기교육개혁법(BR법)이 공표된다. BR 법은 전국의 중학교 3학년 중에서 매년 한 학급을 행동범위가 제한된 일반인이 없는 장소에 이송하여 지도와 일정의 음식, 그리고 여러 가지 무기를 나눠 주고, 마지막 한 사람이 남을 때까지 서로 죽이게 한다는 법률. 제한 시간 3일 동안 위법 행위에 구애받지 않고 서로를 죽여야 한다. 수학여행을 위장하여 무인도에 도착한 학생들은 마치 게임처럼 진행되는 상황에 경악하지만, 생존을 위해 결국 서로의 목숨을 빼앗기 시작한다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Batalha Real","runtime":113,"tagline":"Você mataria seus melhores amigos?","homepage":"","overview":"Em um futuro próximo, o desemprego disparou e a criminalidade juvenil explodiu perante a recessão econômica. O governo japonês aprova a Lei BR, na qual os alunos da 9ª série são enviados para uma ilha remota, onde serão forçados a caçar e matar uns aos outros até sobrar apenas um sobrevivente."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Кралска битка","runtime":121,"tagline":"42-ма ученици, 3 дни, един самотен остров: Добре дошли на \" Кралска битка\"!","homepage":"","overview":"Група деветокласници от една японска гимназия са отвлечени по време на училищна екскурзия. Оставени на самотен остров, те са принудени от законодателството според акт Б.Р. (съставен от правителството, след като 800,000 деца бойкотират японските училища, поради неспособността на държавата да се справи с икономическия колапс) да участват в така наречената \" Кралска битка\". На всеки един е дадена чанта с произволно подбрани оръжия, няколко порции храна и вода. Разполагат с три дни, в който ще водят битка до смърт по - между си, а накрая трябва да остане само един."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"Pourriez-vous tuer votre meilleur ami ?","homepage":"","overview":"Dans un avenir proche, les élèves de la classe B de 3ème du collège Shiroiwa ont été amenés sur une île déserte par une armée mystérieuse. Un adulte surgit tout à coup devant eux : leur ancien professeur Kitano. Il leur annonce qu'ils vont participer à un jeu de massacre dont la règle consiste à s'entretuer. Seul le dernier des survivants pourra regagner son foyer.  Kitano leur présente deux nouveaux élèves très inquiétants. Des coups de feu retentissent pour convaincre les incrédules. Selon la loi de réforme de l'éducation pour le nouveau siècle, ce sacrifice permettra de former des adultes sains.  Abandonnés chacun à son sort avec de la nourriture et une arme, les adolescents disposent d'un délai de trois jours pour s'entretuer."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":114,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ville du kunne dræbe din bedste ven? 42 tilfældige unge stilles over for dette spørgsmål, da regeringen vedtager en ny radikal lov for at dæmme op for et truende ungdomsoprør. Loven går ud på, at de unge mennesker sendt ud på en øde ø, hvor de bliver udstyret med våben. Og her gælder det om at dræbe eller blive dræbt, idet kun én får lov til at forlade øen i live."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Juego sangriento [バトル・ロワイアル]","runtime":114,"tagline":"¿Puedes matar a tu mejor amigo?","homepage":"","overview":"En el amanecer de un nuevo milenio, el país está al borde del colapso. Millones de personas vagan sin empleo. La violencia en la escuela está descontrolada y adolescentes rebeldes protagonizan boicots masivos. El gobierno contrataca con “Battle Royale”. Cada año, una clase es escogida al azar para que se enfrente, en una isla abandonada, a un cruel juego de supervivencia"},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"大逃殺","runtime":114,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"正當日本面臨崩潰，社會陷入動盪的時候，政府通過一條前所未有的青少年新法例─亦即「BR 法案」(Battle Royale)。在這條法案之下，某高中 42 名學生由暴力? 師 (北野武 飾) 率領，被迫到一個杳無人煙的荒島上，參加一場大逃殺死亡遊戲。這個由軍隊嚴厲監守的行動，學生們都獲分派糧食及千奇百怪的兇器。遊戲目的只有一個：互相殘殺，直至剩下最後一人生還，否則沒有逃生的餘地！為求活命，這班中學生唯有將人類殘酷本性徹底表露，上演一場血花四濺、敵友難分的廝殺混戰！？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"大逃殺","runtime":0,"tagline":"你有殺過好朋友嗎？","homepage":"","overview":"剛進入新世紀，某國卻面臨衰敗。懼怕青少年的大人們，發起了新世紀教育改革法，通稱「BR法」。每年一次，從全國中學中隨機選出一個班級，並在無人島進行一場互相殘殺的遊戲，直到剩下一人為止。城岩中學3年B班的學生們，被以校外教學的名義帶到無人島，在班導北野老師無情的指導下，他們被迫參加這場驚悚的奪命遊戲…。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"เกมนรก โรงเรียนพันธุ์โหด","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"โลกอนาคต ประเทศญี่ปุ่นเกิดภาวะล่มสลาย ตกต่ำถึงขีดสุดในทุก ๆ ด้าน เศรษฐกิจพังนินาศยับเยิน ผู้คนจำนวน 10 กว่าล้านกลายเป็นคนว่างงานในชั่วพริบตา สังคมเสื่อมโทรมทรุดหนัก เด็กและเยาวชนที่ต้องออกจากโรงเรียนกลางคันในปีนี้ มีจำนวน 80,000 คน จำนวนครู-อาจารย์ที่เสียชีวิตในหน้าที่ จากการใช้กำลังรุนแรงภายในโรงเรียน มีมากถึง 1,200 คน ระบบการศึกษาเกิดการเปลี่ยนแปลงอย่างรุนแรง รวมทั้งอาชญากรรมที่ก่อขึ้นโดยวัยรุ่น ก็ปรากฏขึ้นมากมาย อาชญากรรมระบาดแพร่หลายไปทั่วทุกหนแห่ง ปัญหาวัยรุ่นกลายเป็นหนึ่งในปัญหาหลักระดับชาติ พวกเขาไม่ยอมเคารพเชื่อฟังคำสั่งของผู้ใหญ่ กระด้างกระเดื่องต่อครูบาอาจารย์ รัฐบาลจึงวางมาตรการตอบโต้ ด้วยการประกาศ \"วิธีการปฏิรูปการศึกษายุคใหม่\" ออกมา ซึ่งมีเป้าหมายเพื่อคืนสิทธิ์ให้กับผู้ใหญ่ โดยใช้เกม \"Battle Royale\" หรือที่เรียกสั้น ๆ ว่า BR มากำราบเด็กแสบ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Cuộc Chiến Sống Còn","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Battle Royale - Batoru rowaiaru là một bộ phim phiêu lưu, bạo lực của Nhật Bản sản xuất năm 2000, được chuyển thể từ cuốn tiểu thuyết cùng tên của tác giả Koushun Takami. Đây cũng chính là bộ phim cuối cùng do Kinji Fukasaku làm đạo diễn. Bộ phim đã gây ra sự tranh cãi và đã bị cấm hoặc loại trừ khỏi việc phân phối ở một số quốc gia. Thậm chí đến nay nhiều người vẫn lầm tưởng Mỹ cấm không cho phát hành bộ phim này tại đất nước mình nhưng thực ra là người Nhật, chính xác là công ty Toei đã từ chối bán bán bản quyền bộ phim này cho bất kỳ nhà phân phối nào tại Hoa Kỳ trong một thời gian dài, bởi vì công ty Toei lo lắng về những tranh cãi và vụ kiện tiềm ẩn về sau (cho đến khi Anchor Bay Entertainment cuối cùng cũng đã được mua lại bộ phim vào năm 2010 để phát hành dưới dạng video trực tuyến)."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Королівська битва","runtime":114,"tagline":"Чи зможеш ти вбити свого найкращого друга?","homepage":"","overview":"\"Королівська битва\" - санкціонована урядом жорстока гра, у якій некерованих школярів змусять брати участь під дулами армійських автоматів. На незаселеному острові 42 підлітки будуть 3 дні безжалісно знищувати один одного, щоб перемогти. Тільки одному гравцеві дозволено повернутися на велику землю живим. Незворушний розпорядник лихозвісної гри - шкільний учитель Кітано."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"სამეფო ბრძოლა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"სამეფო ბრძოლა არის მთავრობის მიერ სანქცირებული ძალადობრივი თამაში, რომელშიც სკოლის მოსწავლეები იძულებულნი არიან მონაწილეობა მიიღონ განადგურების საფრთხის ქვეშ. 42 საშუალო სკოლის მოსწავლე აგზავნიან უკაცრიელ კუნძულზე, სადაც მათ უნდა დახოცონ ერთმანეთი ყველაფრით, რაც ხელთ მოემართებათ - ავტომატური პისტოლეტიდან დაწყებული ტაფამდე. შეიძლება იყოს მხოლოდ ერთი გამარჯვებული."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Борба до последњег","runtime":122,"tagline":"Да ли можете убити најбољег друга?","homepage":"","overview":"Радња се дешава у Јапану у будућности. У стању модерног безосећајног друштва, сваке године се бира по једно одељење од 9 разреда које под мистериозним околностима бива пребачено на једно напуштено острво. Онда почиње акт под називом \"Борба до последњег\"), у којем победник као награду добија живот. Свако добија по једно оружје и распоређују се дуж острва."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":113,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":113,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"","iso_639_1":"nn","iso_3166_1":"NN","english_name":"Norwegian Nynorsk"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":113,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Et Japan herjet av økonomisk nedgang, kaos og en ungdomsgenerasjon ute av kontroll ruller dommedagstungt inn i det nye millenniet. Staten smeller jernneven i bordet og griper inn i et forsøk på å få bukt med rebelske og voldelige skoleelever. Den radikale reformen Battle Royale innføres: hvert år velges en tilfeldig skoleklasse ut, dopes ned og transporteres til en øde øy. Der utstyres de med eksplosive halslenker, matrasjoner og hvert sitt tilfeldige våpen. Deretter er oppgaven enkel: drep alle andre! Det er ingen regler. Alt er lov. Men det er bare én vinner - den som fremdeles står levende igjen til slutt. Og som en liten ekstra motivasjonsfaktor for å få blodtørsten på topp: er mer enn én fremdeles levende etter tre dager detoneres halslenkene, og alle dør."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Kraljevska bitka","runtime":0,"tagline":"Možeš li ubiti svog najboljeg prijatelja?","homepage":"","overview":"Kontroverzni japanski film koji prikazuje distopijsku budućnost u kojoj japanska vlada, kao odgovor na porast nasilja među mladima, organizira godišnji događaj u kojem je klasa srednjoškolaca prisiljena međusobno se boriti na napuštenom otoku dok ne ostane samo jedan preživjeli. Opremljeni raznim oružjem i eksplozivnim ogrlicama, učenici se suočavaju s moralnim dilemama i borbom za preživljavanje u brutalnom okruženju."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Battle Royale","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Actiunea are loc undeva in viitor, guvernul japonez captureaza o clasa de liceeni si ii forteaza sa se ucida unul pe celalalt, totul in spiritul revolutionarului joc Battle Royale. Este filmul care a inspirat \"The Hunger Games\" (2012)."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Karališkas Mūšis","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Artimoje ateityje smarkiai išaugęs jaunimo nusikalstamumas paskatina Japonijos vyriausybę rengti „Karališką mūšį“. Kasmet atsitiktinai parinkta devintokų klasė priverčiama dalyvauti žiauriame žaidime: tris dienas jie paliekami atokioje saloje su ant kaklo uždėtais sprogmenimis. Jie turi kovoti tarpusavyje, nes nugalėtojas yra tik vienas."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":3177,"adult":false,"title":"Battle Royale II: Requiem","video":false,"overview":"It's three years after the events of the original Battle Royale, and Shuya Nanahara is now an internationally-known terrorist determined to bring down the government. His terrorist group, Wild Seven, stages an attack that levels several buildings in Tokyo on Christmas Day, killing 8000 people. In order for the government to study the benefits of \"teamwork\", the new students work in pairs, with their collars electronically linked so that if one of them is killed, the other dies as well. They must kill Nanahara in three days - or die.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.224,"vote_count":522,"poster_path":"/sKoVS6wVmIY0fCDcJYZZ1y3yOK3.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-05","vote_average":4.977,"backdrop_path":"/5BCPhT1zOsSJzeBU7CenRfO6YwL.jpg","original_title":"バトル・ロワイアルII 鎮魂歌","original_language":"ja"},{"id":3989,"adult":false,"title":"Team America: World Police","video":false,"overview":"When North Korean ruler Kim Jong-il orchestrates a global terrorist plot, it's up to the heavily armed, highly specialized Team America unit to stop his dastardly scheme. The group, which has recruited troubled Broadway actor Gary Johnston, not only has to face off against Jong-il, but they must also contend with the Film Actors Guild, a cadre of Hollywood liberals at odds with Team America's 'policing the world' tactics.","genre_ids":[12,28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.037,"vote_count":2004,"poster_path":"/m1Q2VFe1DVVbjfu1LDZe7tlp9yb.jpg","release_date":"2004-10-10","vote_average":6.736,"backdrop_path":"/splQED8WZ5M5OEqDCwZYAAtguZe.jpg","original_title":"Team America: World Police","original_language":"en"},{"id":13550,"adult":false,"title":"The Changeling","video":false,"overview":"After a tragic event happens, composer John Russell moves to Seattle to try to overcome it and build a new and peaceful life in a lonely big house that has been uninhabited for many years. But, soon after, the obscure history of such an old mansion and his own past begin to haunt him.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1337,"vote_count":704,"poster_path":"/z4nTYj3JZ5jWAhDgrmEhW2GRAzb.jpg","release_date":"1980-03-28","vote_average":6.968,"backdrop_path":"/r4nx6BZY4PfLPrThytBtAuwN8uV.jpg","original_title":"The Changeling","original_language":"en"},{"id":3509,"adult":false,"title":"A Scanner Darkly","video":false,"overview":"An undercover cop in a not-too-distant future becomes involved with a dangerous new drug and begins to lose his own identity as a result.","genre_ids":[16,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.6457,"vote_count":1893,"poster_path":"/lUKudOpHICDj6A6SO7DdaZM4W48.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-07","vote_average":6.797,"backdrop_path":"/do8idarfaUTxxwaarefTNA724Qj.jpg","original_title":"A Scanner Darkly","original_language":"en"},{"id":146243,"adult":false,"title":"Haunt","video":false,"overview":"An introverted teen sparks with his new neighbor, and together the couple begins to explore the haunted house that his family has unknowingly just purchased.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5233,"vote_count":245,"poster_path":"/8WusI9Anntdu3yMKir1zPM2Vhka.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-27","vote_average":5.259,"backdrop_path":"/21AC1SV8rVwYIA1J4NbWQNLCTJI.jpg","original_title":"Haunt","original_language":"en"},{"id":37024,"adult":false,"title":"Ranma 1/2 the Movie: Big Trouble in Nekonron, China","video":false,"overview":"When Prince Kirin of the 7 Lucky Gods shows up at the Tendo dojo looking for his bride-to-be, guess who's accidentally holding the scroll that signifies his future mate? Why, Akane, of course, and the rest of the Ranma crew is forced to take a boat to China in order to save her from the horrors of marriage and a diet of pickled vegetables.","genre_ids":[16,35,28,10749,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4437,"vote_count":113,"poster_path":"/2dB9Cx6dXIwr7Hx1jhnADOzwrLC.jpg","release_date":"1991-11-02","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/2jlmBNJrsZnKoBWUtUVkil9iyXO.jpg","original_title":"らんま½ 劇場版 中国寝崑崙大決戦!掟やぶりの激闘篇!!","original_language":"ja"},{"id":241863,"adult":false,"title":"As the Gods Will","video":false,"overview":"High school student Shun Takahata is bored. Bored with the day-to-day monotony of school and life, he prays for change, for something exciting. Suddenly, he and his classmates are forced to play deadly children's games and facing terrifying creatures from a talking Daruma doll to a sharp-clawed lucky cat.","genre_ids":[53,27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8782,"vote_count":555,"poster_path":"/3Obn9IR47fjhbtYtNrO7CBSrZ2w.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-15","vote_average":7.117,"backdrop_path":"/uwZJ4tEgmjKomPPbiimrhHT9l90.jpg","original_title":"神さまの言うとおり","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8326,"adult":false,"title":"Holes","video":false,"overview":"After being wrongfully convicted for stealing a pair of shoes, Stanley Yelnats is sent away to Camp Green Lake, a boys detention facility where inmates are forced to dig holes all day in the hot desert sun as a form of character building. But Stanley and the other boys start to unravel a mystery, linked with the camps tough-as-nails warden —and possibly Stanley’s family itself.","genre_ids":[12,10751,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4761,"vote_count":1508,"poster_path":"/o2Dm2mcE1qW8vT0bpsJO5OMBbqa.jpg","release_date":"2003-04-18","vote_average":6.897,"backdrop_path":"/cVMK2k0Wbs8DV3IK5sS4ziVenrI.jpg","original_title":"Holes","original_language":"en"},{"id":9741,"adult":false,"title":"Unbreakable","video":false,"overview":"An ordinary man makes an extraordinary discovery when a train accident leaves his fellow passengers dead — and him unscathed. The answer to this mystery could lie with the mysterious Elijah Price, a man who suffers from a disease that renders his bones as fragile as glass.","genre_ids":[53,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.4661,"vote_count":9780,"poster_path":"/mLuehrGLiK5zFCyRmDDOH6gbfPf.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-22","vote_average":7.142,"backdrop_path":"/A7CYNTa3fWyU0t207XiecgriQv5.jpg","original_title":"Unbreakable","original_language":"en"},{"id":7340,"adult":false,"title":"Carrie","video":false,"overview":"Withdrawn and sensitive teenager Carrie White faces bullying from classmates and abuse from her fanatically pious mother. When she begins to suspect that she has supernatural powers, things take a dark and violent turn.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6928,"vote_count":4223,"poster_path":"/8tT1rqlsTguyfUBMrbHR9cv1rxM.jpg","release_date":"1976-11-03","vote_average":7.328,"backdrop_path":"/zwJFfKQdfiptK2GY6N8GkZFrAxJ.jpg","original_title":"Carrie","original_language":"en"},{"id":1637,"adult":false,"title":"Speed","video":false,"overview":"Tensions run high when a crazed bomber rigs a Los Angeles bus with a device that will kill everyone on board if the vehicle's speed dips below fifty miles per hour.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.9363,"vote_count":6702,"poster_path":"/82PkCE4R95KhHICUDF7G4Ly2z3l.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-09","vote_average":7.147,"backdrop_path":"/lywmuPU5Hr1Mnpb9UGeDbILmkTx.jpg","original_title":"Speed","original_language":"en"},{"id":11075,"adult":false,"title":"Audition","video":false,"overview":"Seven years after the death of his wife, widower Shigeharu seeks advice on how to find a new wife from a colleague. Taking advantage of their position as a film company, they stage an audition. Interviewing a series of women, Shigeharu is enchanted by the quiet Asami. But soon things take a twisted turn as Asami isn’t what she seems to be.","genre_ids":[27,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2632,"vote_count":1721,"poster_path":"/zwGaUMm0wAqi0wkO7LJDlwoA5LP.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-03","vote_average":7.12,"backdrop_path":"/xmtmZc5aylqDMRKYlU8pmsgG0HF.jpg","original_title":"オーディション","original_language":"ja"},{"id":4291,"adult":false,"title":"Kikujiro","video":false,"overview":"Brash, loudmouthed and opportunistic, Kikujiro is the unlikely companion for Masao who is determined to see the mother he has never met. The two begin a series of adventures which soon turns out to be a whimsical journey of laughter and tears with a wide array of surprises and unique characters along the way.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8591,"vote_count":584,"poster_path":"/zTelT1xAO4Owxk1jHJM4puoei5N.jpg","release_date":"1999-06-05","vote_average":7.499,"backdrop_path":"/rn7i9XrcKtOU6RGhYPukaZTkGNN.jpg","original_title":"菊次郎の夏","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1280,"adult":false,"title":"3-Iron","video":false,"overview":"A drifter lives in people's houses while they are away and repays them by doing chores for them. His life changes when he meets a beautiful woman who wants to escape her unhappy marriage.","genre_ids":[18,10749,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0191,"vote_count":1235,"poster_path":"/myv6rYCghzi2lyWJLbdhZM43JYK.jpg","release_date":"2004-10-15","vote_average":7.82,"backdrop_path":"/nqY8yuxLU4K9cSCQpsW4PGyotlN.jpg","original_title":"빈집","original_language":"ko"},{"id":5910,"adult":false,"title":"Fireworks","video":false,"overview":"Beleaguered police detective Nishi takes desperate measures to try and set things right in a world gone wrong. With his wife suffering from leukemia and his business partner paralyzed from a brutal gangster attack, Nishi borrows from a yakuza loan shark and then robs a bank to clear his debt.","genre_ids":[80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9203,"vote_count":753,"poster_path":"/bWIo1nDJnSyGJvVt8bRw8PHBqo4.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-30","vote_average":7.672,"backdrop_path":"/mdQ6oH7GLM9VerAb8JhsEAyJnHs.jpg","original_title":"HANA-BI","original_language":"ja"},{"id":711,"adult":false,"title":"Finding Forrester","video":false,"overview":"Gus Van Sant tells the story of a young African American man named Jamal who confronts his talents while living on the streets of the Bronx. He accidentally runs into an old writer named Forrester who discovers his passion for writing. With help from his new mentor Jamal receives a scholarship to a private school.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4001,"vote_count":1176,"poster_path":"/chd9bCGNYtzDoJqGw5wUHlhrkOb.jpg","release_date":"2000-12-21","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/eQnIwnhDuHQiSks3dy0zwrJydWU.jpg","original_title":"Finding Forrester","original_language":"en"},{"id":9796,"adult":false,"title":"Turistas","video":false,"overview":"A group of young backpackers' vacation turns sour when a bus accident leaves them marooned in a remote Brazilian rural area that holds an ominous secret.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3017,"vote_count":873,"poster_path":"/nvQqTMPVL8NDeHKEkzAL0ADIECS.jpg","release_date":"2006-12-01","vote_average":5.478,"backdrop_path":"/tgsec2OPZx3l4aoRk4Cdo5cAg9D.jpg","original_title":"Turistas","original_language":"en"},{"id":41428,"adult":false,"title":"Tetsuo: The Iron Man","video":false,"overview":"A \"metal fetishist\", driven mad by the maggots wriggling in the wound he's made to embed metal into his flesh, runs out into the night and is accidentally run down by a Japanese businessman and his girlfriend. The pair dispose of the corpse in hopes of quietly moving on with their lives. However, the businessman soon finds that he is now plagued by a vicious curse that transforms his flesh into iron.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3482,"vote_count":686,"poster_path":"/9RquCMBJ42Kq7ASBy0qcyVP0ugi.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-01","vote_average":6.984,"backdrop_path":"/xt75NSIlfzwPwuBsuarB3i1mBxj.jpg","original_title":"鉄男","original_language":"ja"},{"id":2440,"adult":false,"title":"Joint Security Area","video":false,"overview":"Two North Korean soldiers are killed in the border area between North and South Korea, prompting an investigation by a neutral body. The sergeant is the shooter, but the lead investigator, a Swiss-Korean woman, receives differing accounts from the two sides.","genre_ids":[18,53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.0055,"vote_count":800,"poster_path":"/etoPOj0bXzfw0LBNslCxqO7MHuv.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-09","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/z7w6ACQJTeGYASr1plSwfRe6Ytk.jpg","original_title":"공동경비구역 JSA","original_language":"ko"},{"id":9696,"adult":false,"title":"Ichi the Killer","video":false,"overview":"As sadomasochistic yakuza enforcer Kakihara searches for his missing boss he comes across Ichi, a repressed and psychotic killer who may be able to inflict levels of pain that Kakihara has only dreamed of.","genre_ids":[28,80,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9938,"vote_count":1076,"poster_path":"/k8j4YLZlda98dqp9ErymKzjYowG.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-22","vote_average":6.985,"backdrop_path":"/aw0EeseSr10dVUuY6Aiv6HhP8UW.jpg","original_title":"殺し屋1","original_language":"ja"}],"similar_content":[{"id":313219,"adult":false,"title":"Grasshopper","video":false,"overview":"Movie contains the stories of three people: Suzuki (Toma Ikuta), Kujira (Tadanobu Asano) and Semi (Ryosuke Yamada).  Suzuki is a former middle school teacher. His girlfriend was killed, which led him to quit his job and attempt to take revenge on her murderer. To do so, Suzuki has to infiltrate the underground world of criminals. Kujira is a contract killer for hire. He makes his targets fall into confusion and eventually commit suicide. Semi is a contract killer who uses the knife to take out his targets.","genre_ids":[80,53,28,18],"popularity":0.6663,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/h9YkeTwcSnep0ZvEA6U5KtqCzb5.jpg","release_date":"2015-11-07","vote_average":5.933,"backdrop_path":"/44L1vTmftGyK0aRtKFJMAMHsEc4.jpg","original_title":"グラスホッパー","original_language":"ja"},{"id":48677,"adult":false,"title":"Cloak & Dagger","video":false,"overview":"Davey Osborne is an average 11-year-old boy with an overactive imagination. He spends his days playing video games and pretending to be a spy with his imaginary father-figure, Jack Flack - a substitute for his real father, who is struggling with the recent death of Davey's mother. However, fantasy becomes reality for Davey after he witnesses the murder of an FBI agent, who in his dying breath, gives Davey a mysterious video game cartridge called Cloak & Dagger, which in actuality contains top-secret government information. With the help of his younger friend Kim, the tech savvy Morris, and even a little help from his fictional secret agent mentor, Davey must stay one step ahead of pursuers as he tries to survive a real-life game of espionage in the streets of San Antonio, Texas.","genre_ids":[12,28,10751],"popularity":0.7618,"vote_count":155,"poster_path":"/b7jSCsjZccAwj4nrGXj8XPRAcAc.jpg","release_date":"1984-06-01","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/eF765MoTYrRiXSda5xHVXrFeeQm.jpg","original_title":"Cloak & Dagger","original_language":"en"},{"id":48688,"adult":false,"title":"Pigsty","video":false,"overview":"Two dramatic stories. In an undetermined past, a young cannibal (who killed his own father) is condemned to be torn to pieces by some wild beasts. In the second story, Julian, the young son of a post-war German industrialist, is on the way to lie down with his farm's pigs, because he doesn't like human relationships.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2143,"vote_count":161,"poster_path":"/9FZmcZ9EH4sk9WxLe90m0ddRpnC.jpg","release_date":"1969-09-02","vote_average":7.028,"backdrop_path":"/y5iVIhe8WcGlOOSQu2K72wX7nvl.jpg","original_title":"Porcile","original_language":"it"},{"id":48691,"adult":false,"title":"Goodbye Uncle Tom","video":false,"overview":"Two documentary filmmakers go back in time to the pre-Civil War American South, to film the slave trade.","genre_ids":[18,80,27],"popularity":1.4479,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/nLw410E9rnJw13kufNgOtjiGvGk.jpg","release_date":"1971-09-23","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/qMYvxKZ4ocJbU32bZvFVft7ZjJz.jpg","original_title":"Addio zio Tom","original_language":"it"},{"id":901140,"adult":false,"title":"Impulse","video":false,"overview":"Set in 2020 in the Shibuya neighborhood of Tokyo, the story revolves around Hachi, a boy who fled to the Japanese capital from his hometown of Fukushima and now lives away from society as an illegal drug dealer.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.21,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/f0upvJYkKhJusm8uukIezGx0fJK.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-10","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/lYW9bppE5i3jIomYZL0UWZr6BP9.jpg","original_title":"衝動","original_language":"ja"},{"id":48707,"adult":false,"title":"Shinobi no Mono 2: Vengeance","video":false,"overview":"[Period covered: 1582-1594]. As the film opens, the warlod Nobunaga Oda rides to Iga Ayanokuni shrine. He is asked if he thinks he has destroyed all the ninja who opposed him and answers that he suspects that there may be more. A servant brings water and tests it first. The paige dies and we hear gunshots as two ninja flee the scene. His suspicions confirmed, Nobunaga oversees the execution of captured ninja and decides that, in the future, he needs a much crueler method of execution. The daimyo Hideyoshi comes to visit.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.5159,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/6j7ZNx1SV6aTdxTiJnii07Ex9VK.jpg","release_date":"1963-08-06","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/sHV3Lce8AUAkEgomIp0nQpC5fqc.jpg","original_title":"続・忍びの者","original_language":"ja"},{"id":900783,"adult":false,"title":"The Kashmir Files","video":false,"overview":"Based on a true tragedy, the emotionally triggering film sheds light on the plight of Kashmiri Pandits (Hindus), a religious minority in the 1990s Kashmir valley, who were compelled to flee their homes by the Islamic militants.","genre_ids":[36,18],"popularity":0.5583,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/2VvjJFDBFYkVgr89BjqbUl26QyW.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-11","vote_average":7.012,"backdrop_path":"/o0lQnIaYo5N05mfsltdl3ZCAXpa.jpg","original_title":"द कश्मीर फ़ाइल्स","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1297367,"adult":false,"title":"Remotely Killed: Behind the Scenes of Murder","video":false,"overview":"This is the 58 minutes Hulu version which contains spoiler/reveals throughout the special.","genre_ids":[9648,18],"popularity":0.1713,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/5XzC8T56UFNmYFtijc6ModABdtr.jpg","release_date":"2020-07-26","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/rflAJ2PnTpWPofpcivpZ45yJeyC.jpg","original_title":"リモートで殺される: 殺人の裏側編","original_language":"ja"},{"id":48383,"adult":false,"title":"Samurai Pirate","video":false,"overview":"An adventurous and daring sailor sets sail to the castle of an ailing king to stop an evil premier, hungry for power and wealth, from succeeding the throne and marrying the king's beautiful daughter. Along the way, with the help of some courageous rebels and a lustful wizard, he must overcome the powers of a bewitching witch, a band of ruthless pirates, and the castle's Imperial guards. He must also free those kidnapped into slavery and restore the king's reputation.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,14],"popularity":0.4835,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/mKNjK092wzyaRyQj24DsxO9eaNE.jpg","release_date":"1963-10-26","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/9pVx015TVjWikwp5lO6Xw2kx9IV.jpg","original_title":"大盗賊","original_language":"ja"},{"id":48401,"adult":false,"title":"Pinoy Sunday","video":false,"overview":"The discovery of a discarded sofa, in Taipei city, transforms a routine Sunday into a capricious adventure of perseverance and self-discovery for Filipino guest workers Manuel and Dado.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.4244,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/v7Zrr7mLLASUpMWy47t8ppjB8Ca.jpg","release_date":"2009-10-24","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/wHFPfXoimxvdTC9mNaCACqbzk1l.jpg","original_title":"台北星期天","original_language":"zh"},{"id":513340,"adult":false,"title":"Animals","video":false,"overview":"Longtime friends and party lovers Laura and Tyler navigate life and love in Dublin, Ireland but find themselves drifting apart when Laura becomes engaged.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.5487,"vote_count":51,"poster_path":"/tQyvlLavdNz8xg1vn3Dt7ZC5SnK.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-02","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/sNJ3fBAq37dcx3rbjrMuV8S7bkQ.jpg","original_title":"Animals","original_language":"en"},{"id":513347,"adult":false,"title":"Flavors of Youth","video":false,"overview":"The rigorous city life of China, while bustling and unforgiving, contains the everlasting memories of days past. Three stories told in three different cities, follow the loss of youth and the daunting realization of adulthood. Though reality may seem ever changing, unchangeable are the short-lived moments of one's childhood days. A plentiful bowl of noodles, the beauty of family and the trials of first love endure the inevitable flow of time, as three different characters explore the strength of bonds and the warmth of cherished memories. Within the disorder of the present world, witness these quaint stories recognize the comfort of the past, and attempt to revive the neglected flavors of youth.","genre_ids":[16,10749,18],"popularity":1.0568,"vote_count":578,"poster_path":"/ueHeH5ergeHx27L4SCI9qlmwczA.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-04","vote_average":6.871,"backdrop_path":"/iRB6VKJuFd88bk20hvLqlDzi4kP.jpg","original_title":"肆式青春","original_language":"zh"},{"id":705394,"adult":false,"title":"Nástup","video":false,"overview":"\"The Rally\" is based on a communist writer Vaclav Řezáč's well-written novel of the same name","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1393,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1953-05-01","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Nástup","original_language":"cs"},{"id":705399,"adult":false,"title":"Voices","video":false,"overview":"A troubled young man deals with the competing voices in his head.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1854,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/yOFUDQje4LdGrYVrFwCkEnaNvPF.jpg","release_date":"2020-05-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/qe7OgEW3lA6a95Uh5iD49O0gT8y.jpg","original_title":"Voices","original_language":"en"},{"id":48624,"adult":false,"title":"Urotsukidōji: Legend of the Overfiend","video":false,"overview":"Legend has it that the human race is not the only dominant civilization living on Earth. Two other races exist in this world: the Makai (a demon race) and the Jujinkai (a half-man, half-beast race). Once every 3,000 years, a supreme being known as the Choujin (Overfiend) will emerge and bring balance to all three realms on Earth. In present-day Japan, after 300 years of endless searching, a Jujinkai named Amano Jyaku has discovered the presence of the Choujin inside high school slacker Tatsuo Nagumo. But now, Amano, along with his sister Megumi and their sidekick Kuroko, must protect Nagumo and his new girlfriend Akemi Ito from the Makai, who believe that Nagumo is not the Choujin, but an evil entity bent on destroying all living beings on Earth.","genre_ids":[16,28,27,14],"popularity":3.1238,"vote_count":114,"poster_path":"/5JzDyR3gEkOf1USGIeC8lSOlo3m.jpg","release_date":"1989-03-18","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/1C3Y8XqOxR9LLhKl4BxS5nTTr3C.jpg","original_title":"超神伝説 うろつき童子","original_language":"ja"},{"id":513409,"adult":false,"title":"Earthquake Bird","video":false,"overview":"Tokyo, Japan, 1989. Lucy Fly, a foreigner who works as a translator, begins a passionate relationship with Teiji, a mysterious man obsessed with photography.","genre_ids":[18,9648,10749,53],"popularity":0.8414,"vote_count":460,"poster_path":"/oyKnosHXQ7kkhlGwqsWOvn4RgKR.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-01","vote_average":5.932,"backdrop_path":"/rhklsYtIITDOdFSmhx2fIH9m9Vn.jpg","original_title":"Earthquake Bird","original_language":"en"},{"id":513427,"adult":false,"title":"King Lear","video":false,"overview":"An aging King invites disaster, when he abdicates to his corrupt, toadying daughters, and rejects his loving and honest one.","genre_ids":[18,10770],"popularity":3.1971,"vote_count":102,"poster_path":"/dHd0YS1PGxjfZCVbYi9Hetg7zZd.jpg","release_date":"2018-05-28","vote_average":6.064,"backdrop_path":"/rxYjrlnDWTE8OdhthCfUrEHpUBe.jpg","original_title":"King Lear","original_language":"en"},{"id":513434,"adult":false,"title":"One Cut of the Dead","video":false,"overview":"Real zombies arrive and terrorize the crew of a zombie film being shot in an abandoned warehouse, said to be the site of military experiments on humans.","genre_ids":[35,27,18],"popularity":2.4321,"vote_count":952,"poster_path":"/rws34k2bqYVo2B5MkhKAbV8925j.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-04","vote_average":7.629,"backdrop_path":"/oslUsPw3PUhDVK7a5soTvCAuaO7.jpg","original_title":"カメラを止めるな！","original_language":"ja"},{"id":312962,"adult":false,"title":"The Return","video":false,"overview":"It has been a year since his older brother has left and Willy, fifteen, is waiting impatiently for him to come home. He thinks he knows everything about Théo, but shortly after his return, he discovers a secret about him.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"popularity":1.0974,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/8SOc2s1QJwuSUs6Z8LU8m2rXhds.jpg","release_date":"2014-01-22","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/5YMsRyb0e4ek6IBQcTHMszECS3j.jpg","original_title":"Le retour","original_language":"fr"},{"id":513319,"adult":false,"title":"The Past of Mary Holmes","video":false,"overview":"Mary Holmes (MacKellar), once a famous opera star known as Maria di Nardi, now lives in a run-down shanty and suffers from alcoholism. Known for her eccentric behavior, Mary breeds geese, and is thus known in her neighborhood as 'The Goose Woman'. She blames her grown son Geoffrey (Linden) for the deterioration of her voice, and does everything to destroy his life. When Geoffrey, who works as a commercial artist, announces to her that he will marry Joan Hoyt (Arthur), an actress, she becomes torn with jealousy and threatens to reveal to Joan that he is an illegitimate birth.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2563,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/4QW9sfiM8EJfMJfVnXjJJg2wFKw.jpg","release_date":"1933-01-20","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/pOJjg8gMIBBwDMcV3UCozCPw3MA.jpg","original_title":"The Past of Mary Holmes","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0266308","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q864592","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/battle-royale-2000","mydramalist_id":"9742",